SUMMARY:Design for Longevity: ADUs and Aging in Place
DTSTAMP:20260315T014750Z
DTSTART:20260406T193000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join Lili Weigert\\\, author of Making Space: ADUs for Modern L
	iving\\\, in conversation with local ADU designers Joe Schneider and Mike 
	Freeman of JAS Design Build. They will explore how thoughtful ADU design c
	an support aging in place\\\, foster intergenerational living\\\, and prov
	ide resilient housing options for the future. Rebecca Crichton\\\, Executi
	ve Director of Northwest Center for Creative Aging\\\, will moderate the d
	iscussion.\n\nhttps://townhallseattle.org/event/design-for-longevity/\n\nF
	rom Town Hall Seattle
